  "corrected": "claude",
  "segments": [
    {
      "start": 730.88,
      "end": 731.3,
      "text": "I'm never"
    },
    {
      "start": 731.38,
      "end": 732.34,
      "text": "sure what I'm going to be,"
    },
    {
      "start": 732.7,
      "end": 733.66,
      "text": "from one minute to another!"
    },
    {
      "start": 734.48,
      "end": 734.98,
      "text": "However,"
    },
    {
      "start": 735.18,
      "end": 736.46,
      "text": "I've got back to my right size:"
    },
    {
      "start": 736.82,
      "end": 739.14,
      "text": "the next thing is, to get into that beautiful garden--"
    },
    {
      "start": 739.74,
      "end": 740.76,
      "text": "how _is_ that to be done,"
    },
    {
      "start": 740.9,
      "end": 741.22,
      "text": "I wonder?\""
    },
    {
      "start": 741.7,
      "end": 743.28,
      "text": "As she said this,"
    },
    {
      "start": 743.28,
      "end": 745.28,
      "text": "she came suddenly upon an open place,"
    },
    {
      "start": 745.4,
      "end": 747.42,
      "text": "with a little house in it about four feet"
    },
    {
      "start": 747.52,
      "end": 747.64,
      "text": "high."
    },
    {
      "start": 747.94,
      "end": 749.46,
      "text": "\"Whoever lives there,"
    },
    {
      "start": 749.66,
      "end": 750.2,
      "text": "thought Alice,"
    },
    {
      "start": 750.39,
      "end": 753.0,
      "text": "it'll never do to come upon them _this_ size:"
    },
    {
      "start": 753.28,
      "end": 753.408,
      "text": "why,"
    },
    {
      "start": 754.04,
      "end": 754.18,
      "text": "I"
    },
    {
      "start": 754.24,
      "end": 755.44,
      "text": "should frighten them out of their wits!\""
    },
    {
      "start": 755.68,
      "end": 758.8,
      "text": "So she began nibbling at the right-hand bit again,"
    },
    {
      "start": 758.98,
      "end": 759.54,
      "text": "and"
    },
    {
      "start": 759.6,
      "end": 761.7,
      "text": "did not venture to go near the house till she"
    },
    {
      "start": 761.7,
      "end": 764.2,
      "text": "had brought herself down to nine inches high."
    },
    {
      "start": 766.26,
      "end": 767.18,
      "text": "End of chapter 5"
    }
  ]
}